{"type": "article", "id": 2882, "title": "Alessandro Isola旋转式水槽", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-16T07:54:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232317TmW4pPqzyVZ16SG3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t继成功设计了咖啡桌与地毯书桌之后，Alessandro Isola 又将目光转向卫浴产品。近日，Alessandro Isola 设计了一款名为“ Orbit Sink ”的卫浴产品，由白色可丽耐面材制作而成，基础造型是一个个看上去堆叠争气的圆柱体，使用时，每一层的金属支点都可以保证每一个圆柱形的容器具有旋转功能，开合方便，储存空间丰富。顶层容器下方配有一个镀铬环，相当于一个简易的毛巾架。不规则的设计使得水槽成为了浴室的焦点。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232315bFygNiYm3wUs1rVd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232316QklRGtoN63IKq2fv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232316UPJNbvC5SA0fMgVr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232316ZhviK3GanQTr5loM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}